v0.2.0
    - adding global support via `npm install -g grunt-devtools`
    - adding target support in the UI
    - added color log support
    - style and formatting fixes
    - other bug fixes
    - adding experimental Brackets support
v0.1.0.7
    - Fixes, added update warnings.
v0.1.0.6
    - Various fixes.
v0.1.0.5
    - Updating UI
    - Adding a way to set flags `--force` and `--verbose`
    - output fixes
    - background task updates.
v0.1.0.4
    - Adding Background Task support. You can now press `(B)` to send the task into background and continue running other tasks.
v0.1.0-alpha3
    - Adds `Gruntfile.coffee` support
